cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about natural language processing and word embedding. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a scalable Bayesian neural word embedding algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with advanced methods for word embedding. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a potential category as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach for word embedding. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the proposed algorithm can be beneficial for general item similarity tasks, which can include image similarity tasks.
